Title: Cinderella 2: Dreams Come True
Writer: Jill E. Blotevogel (screenplay), Eddie Guzelian (interstitials written by), Eddie Guzelian (screenplay), Tom Rogers (screenplay), Jule Selbo (screenplay), Tom Rogers (screenplay)
Actors: Jennifer Hale, Rob Paulsen, Corey Burton, Andre Stojka
Plot: Jaq and Gus create a storybook based on three events that happened after the first film. The stories include Cinderella's opposition to the court's strict etiquette, Jaq's becoming human for a day, and Anastasia's redemption through love.
